data.description: Isn't she lovely? This beautiful 4 bedroom 2 bathroom recently updated split level is sure to please. Updates include but are not limited to: new flooring, lighting, addition of a primary bedroom walk in closet, gorgeous new electric fireplace, kitchen cabinet refresh and new tile backsplash, just to name a few. In addition to all the updates, this home sits on corner lot in a beautiful mature neighborhood.  Don't wait on this one, call for a showing today!
